      <item>
        <title>Website Initial Load time is too long</title>
        <dc:creator><![CDATA[cristianbote]]></dc:creator>
        <description><![CDATA[
            <p>Hi <a class="mention" href="https://community.frontity.org/u/santoshdevnath15">@santoshdevnath15</a>,</p>
<p>As <a class="mention" href="https://community.frontity.org/u/juanma">@juanma</a> noted a repo or CodeSandbox will help a lot with solving these kind of issues.</p>
<p>Looking at the transferred network size indeed, is around <code>~80kB</code> but the actual document is <code>1MB</code> in size. With a vanilla mars-theme the document size is <code>330kB</code>, so that makes me think that there’s something going on your theme code, which is outputting more html than necessary.</p>
<p></p><div class="lightbox-wrapper"><a class="lightbox" href="https://community.frontity.org/uploads/default/original/2X/6/6c459b45df8c61f1be107b3d92168cbcd7b5b25d.png" data-download-href="https://community.frontity.org/uploads/default/6c459b45df8c61f1be107b3d92168cbcd7b5b25d" title="Screenshot 2021-05-11 at 10.05.38"><img src="https://community.frontity.org/uploads/default/optimized/2X/6/6c459b45df8c61f1be107b3d92168cbcd7b5b25d_2_690x282.png" alt="Screenshot 2021-05-11 at 10.05.38" data-base62-sha1="frOHhzYiH1XV09K31kA5T3lIYaN" width="690" height="282" srcset="https://community.frontity.org/uploads/default/optimized/2X/6/6c459b45df8c61f1be107b3d92168cbcd7b5b25d_2_690x282.png, https://community.frontity.org/uploads/default/original/2X/6/6c459b45df8c61f1be107b3d92168cbcd7b5b25d.png 1.5x, https://community.frontity.org/uploads/default/original/2X/6/6c459b45df8c61f1be107b3d92168cbcd7b5b25d.png 2x" data-small-upload="https://community.frontity.org/uploads/default/optimized/2X/6/6c459b45df8c61f1be107b3d92168cbcd7b5b25d_2_10x10.png"></a></div><p></p>
<p>Try it out with a vanilla mars-theme and see if the size changes.</p>
          <p><a href="https://community.frontity.org/t/website-initial-load-time-is-too-long/4531/6">Read full topic</a></p>
